      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "dd2d9bd8efee8e08",
      "text": "Willy talks about **connection as Love**. It seems that humans may be afraid of Love. Can we love all creatures? I know I can connect with the ones that are open to it when I am open too."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
