      "text": "We can regard **discord** as a homeostat. I experienced dissonance with some trainers I visited with my horses. They would be telling me that what they were seeing was good but it felt bad to me. I couldn't understand it and felt it was maybe a problem with my judgement. We need to explore why together."
    },
